Package: dx-vnpu-rt-ep
Architecture: arm64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: DeepX VNPU Runtime Environment Package
 DeepX VNPU Runtime Environment Package provides runtime libraries
 and executables for DeepX Neural Processing Unit (NPU).
 This package includes the runtime libraries, command-line tools,
 and ONNX Runtime support for ARM64 architecture.
